Text: RE New BEL GAS PHY OPT Customer Profiles Cc Imelda Bel Gas Phy Option product customer profile list approved from credit Gabriel Original Message From Frayre Imelda Sent October To Boyd Justin Harrison Oliver Cc Brungs Ian Maley Paul Enron London EOL Product Control Group Harris Annette Subject New BEL GAS PHY OPT Customer Profiles Hi Guys The trader has confirmed that they want to copy the existing customer profiles for Bel Gas Phy ZEE HUB to the new Bel Gas Phy Option product types below Can you please let me know if this will be okay If new profiles will need to be created let me know and I will send you a spreadsheet of the existing profiles for the physical product type so you can amend them accordingly for the option product types Thanks Imelda Original Message From Frayre Imelda Sent October To Boyd Justin Harrison Oliver Hill Gail Patel Jitendra RAC Market Risk Shah Rajen Harris Annette OHare Christine Howard Stephanie Allan Matthew Dautel Rudy Oliver Jennifer Cc Juggins Janine Brungs Ian Maley Paul Enron London EOL Product Control Group McKinney Lara EOL Marketing Europe Subject New BEL GAS PHY OPT Product Types All Annette Harris wishes to put new products out on EnronOnline The product types are as follows Product Type Bel Gas Phy Call Option Zee Hub Product Type Bel Gas Phy Put Option Zee Hub Launch Date Novermber Attached are the GTCs that will be used and the product type launch timetable which details what needs to be done by the different departments The approved long descriptions will be sent out shortly Please foward this message to any other key people I have left off the distribution list Regards Imelda Frayre EnronOnline PCG
